snippet.title: #JohnnyDepp  & Amber Heard Case : Narcissistic Abuse?
snippet.description:
Dropping back in n this case. You guys have really kept me informed and I came back to take a peek at how things were going .  This toxic relationship had lots of traits in it that go along with Narcissism. I of course can’t diagnose anyone but I can talk about the traits. Whew, it was exhausting just hearing about their relationship . Johnny Depp will be much happier when he is done having to deal with this stuff. He can then begin to heal. These kinds of relationships take a long time to heal from. Trauma work for CPTSD I think may be needed.  I mean he had the tip of his finger cut  off! 😱 What do you guys see happening next? Have you ever been in a toxic relationship before? Was this triggering for you?
#justiceforjohnny #johnnydepp #amberheard #narcissist #npd #narcissistictraits #amberheard
